      <title>价值 2.38 亿美元的惊喜礼物之谜震惊佛罗里达学校</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/mystery-behind-238-million-surprise-gift-roils-florida-school</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在佛罗里达农业机械大学，今年的毕业典礼带来了一个引人注目的转折：这所拥有 136 年历史的黑人公立学校获得了 2.38 亿美元的捐赠。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/mystery-behind-238-million-surprise-gift-roils-florida-school</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 17:19:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
